## Workflow

### Step 1: User Requests Analysis

```
User: "Analyze [YouTube channel]"
```

### Step 2: Activate YouTube Channel Analysis Skill

Reference: `/agent-skills-library/cursor-rules/youtube-channel-analysis/RULE.md`

1. Gather user context (niche, goals, etc.)
2. Check if data is collected (yt-dlp)
3. Create analysis plan (4-stage pipeline)
4. Execute phases incrementally
5. Generate personalized recommendations

### Step 3: Save Outputs

All reports save to `reports/` directory in this project.

